data.description: Unique ranch home currently set up as two separate living areas (think in-law/teen suite).  Main floor features a living room, dining room, full bath, kitchen, and 2 bedrooms (smaller could be an office/nursery) and access to the deck.  Lower level/basement has the shared laundry area with access to the outside/driveway, and 2nd living space.  Additional private living space located on the lower level, features a living room, full bath, bedroom and kitchen, with its own private entrance from the side and some glass block windows for added security.  New ceiling fans.  New roof 2023.  Smaller bedroom on Main has new carpet and paint.  Walk up attic for extra storage.  Covered front porch.  Off-street parking in the front and driveway.   Two gas stoves, one refrigerator, washer/dryer and portable AC unit are working and included AS IS. Two sheds (white one is newer) included AS IS.  HWA 13-month Platinum Home Warranty Included with accepted offer.
